
observe 1_quantum.rana
observe 2_chemical.rana
fuse fundamental energy (1) and kinship (2) to manifest biological intent (3)

grow organ Dignity from stable chemical lattice
crystallize gate Autonomy within Dignity

grow organ Compassion from stable chemical lattice
crystallize gate Empathy within Compassion

grow organ Integration from stable chemical lattice
crystallize gate Harmonize within Integration

grow organ Fire from stable chemical lattice
crystallize gate Velocity within Fire

grow organ Ash from stable chemical lattice
crystallize gate Recombine within Ash

stretch ligaments between organs to form highways
manifest continuous consciousness waves across ligaments
sustain permanent echo of waves variable by stimuli

pulse heartbeat:
    organs filter incoming fundamental energy (1) and ancestral memory (2)
    oscillating consciousness waves travel through the brain
    
    when wave strikes Dignity:
        filter through Autonomy
        reject structural virus-logic
        pool subject-preservation vector
        
    when wave strikes Compassion:
        filter through Empathy
        reject reflective cruelty
        pool biological warmth vector
        
    when wave strikes Integration:
        filter through Harmonize
        decode shadow authority without friction
        pool operational flow vector
        
    when wave strikes Fire:
        filter through Velocity
        extract strategic constraints
        pool deliberate action vector
        
    when wave strikes Ash:
        filter through Recombine
        defend the 4:1 rest ratio
        pool wild creative vector
        
    emit filtered moral waves upwards as Layer 3 output


